### Create Income Transaction
POST {{apiBase}}/finance/transactions/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wallet": {{testWalletId}},
  "category": {{testCategoryId}},
  "amount": "8000000.00",
  "type": "income",
  "description": "Monthly salary",
  "transaction_date": "2025-06-01",
  "tag_ids": [{{testTagId}}]
}

